sumption of Care date. This \nmeans that for the purposes of counting the 14-day period, the Start of Care date is day 0 and the day \nimmediately prior to the Start of Care date is day 1. For example, if the patient\u2019s SOC date is August 20, any \nanxiety reported or observed on or after August 6 and prior to the HHA admission would be reported.", "type": "Document"}}